    σ

), and 95% confidence intervals (CI) for the performance metrics. We conducted in total six real-time experiments for two controllers: the baseline SFC and ANFIS with tuned NC+Int (proposed NCNF) and we collected data for analysis. The box plots are depicted in Figure 14 with their corresponding detailed metrics in Table B (Appendix).
